originalText.text: Dr DePorto treated me for multiple years following my brain injury. Every NYU staff member who treated me said that he was the best Dr NYU Rusk Rehabilitation had. As one member of my treatment team said, "he's the best diagnostician and no one fights harder for his patients." He's compassionate, insightful, innovative.  Without him my recovery would have far more limited.
